Subject: drm/amdgpu: allow pinning DMA-bufs into VRAM if all importers can do
 P2P
Mime-version: 1.0
Content-type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-transfer-encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f5e7fabd1f5c65b2e077efcdb118cfa67eae7311
